OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FAn ex-head gamekeeper has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor a minimum of 19 years after
OL,9,Fmurdering a former colleague with a
OL,10,Fshotgun on a country track in
OL,11,FScotland, after police almost ruled
OL,12,Fthe death non-suspicious.
OL,14,FDavid Campbell, 77, killed Brian Low,
OL,15,F65, on February 16 2024, having
OL,16,Fpreviously disabled CCTV cameras at
OL,17,Fhis home in Aberfeldy in an attempt to
OL,18,Fconceal his whereabouts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FBoth men had worked at Edradynate
OL,8,FEstate, where Campbell was head
OL,9,Fgamekeeper between May 1984 and
OL,10,FFebruary 2018, and Mr Low was a
OL,11,Fgroundsman between August 2000 and
OL,12,FFebruary 2023.
OL,14,FCampbell attacked Mr Low while the
OL,15,Fformer groundsman was walking his dog
OL,16,Fat Leafy Lane near Pitilie. Mr Low was
OL,17,Fso severely injured that he died at
OL,18,Fthe scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FMr Low was shot at about 4.52pm on
OL,8,FFebruary 16 and his body was found by
OL,9,Fa local man at about 8.30am the
OL,10,Ffollowing day.
OL,12,FPolice made a series of blunders,
OL,13,Fwhich meant Campbell was not arrested
OL,14,Funtil three months after the killing.
OL,16,FHanding him a minimum sentence of 19
OL,17,Fyears, the judge said Mr Campbell had
OL,18,Fcommitted a "senseless act of extreme
OL,19,Fwickedness".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FDuring the nearly three-week trial,
OL,8,Fthe court heard Campbell had harboured
OL,9,Fa "festering grievance" against Mr
OL,10,FLow, believing him to have planted
OL,11,Fevidence on the estate to frame him
OL,12,Ffor the alleged illegal poisoning of
OL,13,Fbirds of prey.
OL,15,FOn the day of the murder, after
OL,16,Fdisabling the CCTV cameras at his
OL,17,Fhome, Campbell travelled to the scene
OL,18,Fof the killing on his wife's e-bike,
OL,19,Fwearing a "hooded jacket" and armed
OL,20,Fwith a shotgun carried in a bag slung
OL,21,Fon his back.
OL,26,@qD@COUqD@WO]{D@KOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FCampbell was found guilty on Wednesday
OL,8,Ffollowing a trial at the High Court in
OL,9,FGlasgow, and was sentenced at the same
OL,10,Fcourt shortly afterwards.
OL,12,FFollowing the verdict, Detective Chief
OL,13,FSuperintendent Lorna Ferguson said she
OL,14,Fhad apologised to Mr Low's family
OL,15,Fpersonally for failings in the
OL,16,Finvestigation, which led to his death
OL,17,Fbeing treated as non-suspicious for
OL,18,Fseveral days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThis was even though he suffered about
OL,8,F30 injuries from shotgun pellets, and
OL,9,Fthose pellets fell from his body bag
OL,10,Fwhen it was brought to a mortuary.
OL,12,FJailing Campbell for life with a
OL,13,Fminimum term of 19 years, judge Lord
OL,14,FScott described the killing as an
OL,15,F"appalling and senseless act of
OL,16,Fextreme wickedness".
OL,18,FHe told Campbell: "You didn't
OL,19,Fencounter Brian Low by chance that
OL,20,Fday, and you didn't happen to have a
OL,21,Fshotgun with you.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@SO]zD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"On the evidence, the jury decided
OL,8,Fthat it was proved beyond reasonable
OL,9,Fdoubt that in a carefully premeditated
OL,10,Fact, you murdered an unarmed and
OL,11,Fdefenceless man by discharging a
OL,12,Fshotgun at him, causing him such
OL,13,Fsevere injury that he died where he
OL,14,Ffell."
OL,16,FLord Scott also referred to victim
OL,17,Fimpact statements from Mr Low's
OL,18,Fpartner Pam Curran and brother Douglas
OL,19,FLow, and said his murder had had a
OL,20,F"profound and lasting" impact on his
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@FO]|D@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
