PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHe told Campbell he had "robbed" Ms
OL,8,FCurran of the chance to say goodbye to
OL,9,FMr Low, and that a friend had told her
OL,10,Fthat since his death "the spark has
OL,11,Fgone out of her eyes".
OL,13,FThe judge added: "Brian Low's family
OL,14,Fare left with only questions, not
OL,15,Fleast why anyone would want to murder
OL,16,Fhim so callously."
OL,26,@oD@YOUoD@`O]rD@VOUsD@UO]uD@ROUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
