PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FCampbell, who appeared in court
OL,8,Fdressed in a dark-coloured suit,
OL,9,Fshowed no reaction as the sentence was
OL,10,Fhanded down, and blew a kiss to the
OL,11,Fpublic gallery as he was being led
OL,12,Faway.
OL,14,FIn his closing speech on Friday,
OL,15,Fprosecutor Greg Farrell told the jury:
OL,16,F"There, using his shotgun he shot
OL,17,FBrian Low, hitting him on the face,
OL,18,Fchest and neck, and left him for dead.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
