PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"Brian Low was out with his dog
OL,13,FMillie, going about his ordinary
OL,14,Fpeaceful life. He was left to die on
OL,15,Fthat track alone.
OL,17,F"That shotgun blast killed him within
OL,18,Fminutes or perhaps seconds. Brian Low
OL,19,Fhad no chance. He was unarmed and
OL,20,Funaware.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772121849
OL,3,CEx-gamekeeper who shot former
OL,4,Ccolleague on remote Highlands path
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"This was a brazen, brutal and planned
OL,8,Fexecution at a rural spot, a cowardly
OL,9,Fambush motivated by nothing more than
OL,10,Fsheer malice."
OL,12,FCampbell initially faced a total of
OL,13,Feight charges but on Friday seven of
OL,14,Fthese were withdrawn, leaving just the
OL,15,Fsingle charge of murder.
OL,17,FCampbell had denied murder, claiming
OL,18,Fhe was at home in Aberfeldy at the
OL,19,Ftime of the murder, but this was
OL,20,Frejected by the jury.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@NO]
